			Le Cinque
			=========

A game for learning beginner Italian vocabulary, five words at a
time.  Play it at https://le-cinque.pages.dev -- buono studio!

CURRICULUM

  Five Italian words are laid out with their English translations
  hidden.  Fill in the letters to reveal all five before you run out
  of mistakes.  Over 1,500 everyday words, with spaced repetition so
  the ones you miss come back later.

BUILDING

  The API is a Go service in api/; the web client lives in web/ and
  is built with Bun.

    bun run dev:api      start the API
    bun run dev:web      start the web client
    bun run test:api     run the API tests
    bun run test:web     run the web tests
    bun run build:web    build the web client
